               <scopecontent id="aspace_cf289df6263ccffc0e58f2e29668db40">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Part 4 covers Knapp's life after divorce, his move to Guilford, Connecticut, senior years, joining gay or gay friendly organizations, his relationship with his boyfriend, hiking, sailing, the Stonewall Speakers, the First Congregational Church of Guilford, GLSEN, being expelled from the BSA, publicity surrounding his expulsion, his activism, and Scouting for All.</p>
